                                                ./functions/notify.in.absentia/t

    ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

      /create.participant     Contains code that creates a file on disk for participant
                              credentials.

      t   create.participant                    No references.

          create.participant.gylf.command       No references.

          build.pouch                           ./functions/create.participant/t

          build.pouch.increment.byte            ./functions/create.participant/t

